title: SEC Shorts - Auburn and Texas A&M show up early to claim their wins
author: SEC Shorts
description: Auburn and Texas A&M get a head start on post game traffic and head to the Wins Claim Department in order to claim their W's for this week. Just one tiny problem, the clock hasn't struck zero yet. No way this comes back to haunt them right? Right?
